jUIRTE

A really simple (and light) Rich Text Editor (wysiwyg) for Jquery UI

== Featuring: ==
* Buttons & Buttonsets
* Expandable
* Cross-browser
* Very,very,very,very SMALL!

== To-Do ==
* Fix scroll bars in IE
* Fix items showing below textarea being hidden because no real wrapper
* Hook up all other buttons - ie links/unlink, colors etc
* Add spacers that seperate buttonsets
* Add menu rows

== Example == 
$(document).ready(function(){ 
 $("#myEditor").wysiwyg();
});

